data.description: Move Right In to This Spacious Updated Home with Private Treed Backyard! Kitchen & All 3 Bathrooms are Remodeled, New Flooring, Paint, Light Fixtures/ Switches/ Covers, Fans, & Stainless Steel Appliances.  Newly Designed Kitchen was Opened Up to Great Room with Cozy Fireplace & 3 BR's Plus 2 Full Baths on Main Level and All Solid Surface Flooring Throughout!  Finished Walkout Basement with 4th BR & 3rd Full Bath, Laundry and Flex Room (Could be a 5th Non-Conforming BR). Deck off Kitchen w/ Stairs Down to Patio & Grilling Space. New AC & Tankless Water Heater.
